OL,6,GWould anyone care to place bets on the
OL,7,Governight ratings for the final episode
OL,8,Gof Happy Valley?
OL,10,FYet again, reports of the death of
OL,11,Flinear television have been much
OL,12,Fexaggerated. Incredibly the overnight
OL,13,Fratings have actually climbed as the
OL,14,Fseries progressed. Last week's episode
OL,15,Fscored above 6m viewers for the first
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,18,FIt's a perfect example of linear TV and
OL,19,Fthe iPlayer working together
OL,20,Fpositively.
OL,3,CStriking a balance between linear TV
OL,4,Cand streaming
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/9
