OL,6,FBut so too is the iPlayer ` it's great
OL,7,Ffor those of us who can't watch on
OL,8,FSundays or who came late to the party.
OL,10,FIt's the perfect example of a mixed
OL,11,Feconomy ` especially for the public
OL,12,Fservice broadcaster where the incentive
OL,13,Fis to serve audiences rather than
OL,14,Fgenerate income.
OL,16,FThe overall ratings for Happy Valley
OL,17,Fare even higher once iPlayer downloads
OL,18,Fare included.
OL,3,CStriking a balance between linear TV
OL,4,Cand streaming
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
