OL,6,FBrilliant as the iPlayer is, would
OL,7,FHappy Valley score anything like these
OL,8,Foverall numbers if it wasn't "dropping"
OL,9,Fat the same time on BBC One?
OL,11,FThis all stands in contrast to ITV's
OL,12,Fbig drama of the week.
OL,14,FNolly, the story of Noele Gordon and
OL,15,Fher sacking from Crossroads, has been
OL,16,Favailable to binge watch on ITVX since
OL,17,FThursday. It's a terrific watch which
OL,18,Fhas earned rave reviews.
OL,20,FITV still hasn't said how many people
OL,21,Fhave watched it.
OL,3,CStriking a balance between linear TV
OL,4,Cand streaming
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
