OL,6,FBut one thing is certain. When it
OL,7,Fappears on ITV 1 later in the year, the
OL,8,Fovernight ratings are likely to be
OL,9,Frelatively modest. Most of those who
OL,10,Fwere keenest to watch will already have
OL,11,Fseen it.
OL,13,FFor a commercial broadcaster though,
OL,14,Fthe arguments are different. Some of
OL,15,Fthe audiences advertisers want may be
OL,16,Freached more effectively by streaming.
OL,17,FThose who want to watch ad free can
OL,18,Fpay, bringing another revenue stream to
OL,19,FITV.
OL,3,CStriking a balance between linear TV
OL,4,Cand streaming
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
