SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1678145224
OL,6,FBut oh the irony that Nolly should be
OL,7,Fpioneering ITV's move into direct
OL,8,Fcompetition with Netflix and the like.
OL,10,FWhile her story is fascinating ` and
OL,11,Fgood drama can allow us to empathise
OL,12,Fwith characters we are unfamiliar with
OL,13,F` there will be few under 50 who will
OL,14,Fhave heard of Noele Gordon.
OL,16,FHer personal popularity was very much
OL,17,Flinked to the world of linear
OL,18,Fbroadcasting.
OL,3,CStriking a balance between linear TV
OL,4,Cand streaming
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
