OL,6,FThe two programmes she was most
OL,7,Fassociated with ` Lunchbox in the
OL,8,FMidlands and Crossroads nationally `
OL,9,Fwere successes because they were part
OL,10,Fof the everyday lives of viewers.
OL,12,FIf you watch the one surviving edition
OL,13,Fof Lunchbox or a typical episode of
OL,14,FCrossroads you will wonder what the
OL,15,Ffuss was about. They were anything but
OL,16,Fhigh end products where every last shot
OL,17,Fand line were lovingly crafted to
OL,18,Fperfection.
OL,3,CStriking a balance between linear TV
OL,4,Cand streaming
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
