PN,35308
SC,0008
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1678145224
OL,6,FInstead it was the relationship between
OL,7,Fthese programmes and their viewers as
OL,8,Fpart of everyday life which made them
OL,9,Fspecial to Nolly's fans.
OL,11,FBy the way, the surviving episode of
OL,12,FLunchbox includes a curio for Pres
OL,13,Ffans. In the absence of continuity,
OL,14,FNolly trails the afternoon's schools
OL,15,Fprogrammes and the recording appears to
OL,16,Fshow ATV's daytime closing sequence.
OL,18,FMeanwhile those of us who derided
OL,19,FCrossroads (including plenty of
OL,20,Fdiscriminating viewers and the IBA)
OL,21,Fwere left bemused and sometimes even
OL,22,Fconcerned by its popularity.
OL,3,CStriking a balance between linear TV
OL,4,Cand streaming
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/9
