OL,6,FHere's the lesson. It's about the
OL,7,Frelationship between broadcasters and
OL,8,Fviewers' lives. Part of the daily
OL,9,Froutine, something to share with
OL,10,Ffriends, something to talk to strangers
OL,11,Fabout.
OL,13,FThrow away linear TV and you throw away
OL,14,Fsomething special.
OL,3,CStriking a balance between linear TV
OL,4,Cand streaming
